Remember when you cut yourself?

35:42.069 --> 35:44.218
It's all in here.

35:44.322 --> 35:46.261
The hole...

35:46.678 --> 35:48.346
Okay.

35:48.450 --> 35:50.816
The geode.

35:52.538 --> 35:54.685
And look at this.

35:54.790 --> 35:56.959
The levitation.

35:57.064 --> 35:59.418
What's that supposed to prove?

35:59.774 --> 36:02.110
