the sacrifice wasn't complete.

36:52.180 --> 36:56.184
If we had put the offering in the hole,
it would have blown the gate wide open.

36:56.601 --> 36:59.105
I think right now
it's like only open a crack.

36:59.209 --> 37:02.462
They can influence us,
but they can't get through.

37:02.567 --> 37:04.402
It's just...

37:04.506 --> 37:06.591
How can this be true?

37:06.695 --> 37:10.134
