39:10.068 --> 39:12.800
Well, so what's under the door?

39:24.146 --> 39:26.608
See? They're gone.

39:26.712 --> 39:28.275
It worked.

39:28.379 --> 39:30.473
You guys are weird.

39:31.195 --> 39:33.509
