40:28.857 --> 40:31.795
Okay. Houston, ready for liftoff.

40:32.483 --> 40:34.800
- Ready?
- Ready.

40:34.904 --> 40:37.010
Ready, Houston.

40:37.323 --> 40:38.823
Okay.

40:40.472 --> 40:45.248
5, 4, 3, 2, 1!

40:45.352 --> 40:47.281
Blastoff!

40:47.385 --> 40:50.024
Yeah! All right!

40:50.692 --> 40:52.419
Yeah!

40:54.340 --> 40:56.486
That's the best.

40:58.907 --> 41:02.595
- Who's that?
- Well, there's one way to find out.

41:08.250 --> 41:10.479
Demons aren't gonna ring the doorbell.

41:12.588 --> 41:15.411
