Alexandra, what's your problem?

41:37.196 --> 41:40.574
- Hey, don't touch that.
- I'm just looking at it.

41:40.678 --> 41:44.453
Come on, that's my dad's. Put that down.
He never lets us play with it.

41:44.557 --> 41:47.725
Okay, okay. Don't have a cow.

41:54.817 --> 41:56.713
Way to go.

41:58.081 --> 41:59.830
Here.

42:01.407 --> 42:03.541
The thunderbolt.

42:04.014 --> 42:07.980
- She didn't throw it out.
- Hey, are you guys in bed yet?

42:08.085 --> 42:10.790
Almost. Put it back.

42:15.566 --> 42:17.382
What are you doing?

42:17.486 --> 42:20.550
- Probably fagging off.
- What did you do to your face?

42:20.655 --> 42:22.526
None of your beeswax, four-eyes.

42:22.631 --> 42:26.201
- I think it's a definite improvement.
- Hey, eat your feet, dwarf.

42:26.305 --> 42:29.477
- Suck my nose till my head caves in.
- Why don't you grow up?

42:29.581 --> 42:30.947
- Drop dead.
- Up yours!

42:31.051 --> 42:33.981
- Piss off!
- Why don't you just shut up!

42:34.711 --> 42:36.398
Just go to bed.

42:40.384 --> 42:43.001
Did you ever want a brother
or a sister or anything?

42:43.105 --> 42:44.876
Nope.

43:13.615 --> 43:17.075
Indians. Oh, boy.

43:27.087 --> 43:32.312
"Dark Master, demon
of unimaginable size and power."

43:32.842 --> 43:34.393
Terry?

44:26.709 --> 44:29.816
Terry. Terry.

44:29.920 --> 44:32.108
Are you awake?

45:26.477 --> 45:29.356
Al! Al! They're back!

45:29.460 --> 45:31.440
- The moths came back!
- What? What is it?

45:31.544 --> 45:35.626
- They broke the window! They're in my room!
- What are you talking about?

45:39.636 --> 45:41.825
Oh, my gosh.

45:47.852 --> 45:49.602
Terry?

45:52.586 --> 45:54.694
Hey, Terry, wake up.

45:55.632 --> 45:57.318
Terry!

46:01.867 --> 46:05.413
- Terry?
