47:37.302 --> 47:40.025
Glen! Come on!

47:56.231 --> 47:58.285
What are we gonna do?

47:58.389 --> 48:00.295
Back door!

48:04.593 --> 48:06.781
What are we gonna do?

48:07.681 --> 48:09.787
Oh, shoot!

48:09.891 --> 48:13.433
- Hurry up, Al! Hurry up, Al!
- Would you guys shut up?

48:25.885 --> 48:27.990
I don't see anything.

48:31.600 --> 48:33.725
- Come on!
- I'm trying!

48:42.882 --> 48:46.965
- Let me take a look first.
- Good idea.

49:16.395 --> 49:18.917
Al, I think you better come back!

49:19.564 --> 49:21.566
Shut up, you guys!

49:21.670 --> 49:23.255
Al, come back.

49:23.360 --> 49:26.218
What do you want? What is it?

49:28.302 --> 49:30.207
Come on!

49:36.029 --> 49:38.956
- Hurry up!
- Come on, hurry up!

49:41.357 --> 49:43.273
Hurry!

49:44.913 --> 49:46.077
Look.

50:00.299 --> 50:01.962
Are you okay?

50:02.066 --> 50:04.860
- What the hell is going on?
- Somebody knock her out again.

50:04.965 --> 50:07.130
I'm calling the police.

50:11.117 --> 50:13.241
Answer it!

50:31.198 --> 50:32.512
Hello.

50:32.616 --> 50:36.305
<i>You've been bad!</i>

50:47.965 --> 50:51.782
We have to close the gate.
We have to go to the hole and do it right.

50:51.887 --> 50:54.159
You mean, you guys were serious
about that demon stuff?

50:54.263 --> 50:56.576
What does it look like?

50:57.871 --> 51:02.897
- What the hell are you talking about?
