51:07.381 --> 51:08.986
Are you sure we can get rid of them?

51:09.090 --> 51:12.281
Yeah. I've got all the spells
and curses to banish the demons.

51:12.385 --> 51:15.972
- Demons? What kind?
- Don't ask.

51:16.076 --> 51:20.060
- How do you know what to do?
- Just trust me. I know what I'm doing.

51:20.164 --> 51:21.893
Right.

51:25.482 --> 51:28.590
- Al.
- What is it?

51:28.694 --> 51:30.616
Forget it.

51:43.437 --> 51:45.375
Over there.

51:48.880 --> 51:51.736
What? Do they hate music?

52:03.249 --> 52:05.709
Great, now what do we do?

52:05.814 --> 52:08.337
