if we waited inside.

53:12.725 --> 53:14.909
My heroes.

53:34.935 --> 53:37.248
You've got to be kidding.

53:43.256 --> 53:45.300
I hope this works.

53:45.404 --> 53:47.362
Me, too.

53:50.180 --> 53:52.097
Here it goes.

53:52.723 --> 53:56.340
"Deliver me from my enemies,
father in heaven.

53:56.444 --> 54:00.753
"Deliver me from the workers of iniquity.

54:00.857 --> 54:03.786
And save me from the devils of blood."

54:14.913 --> 54:19.919
"Away from my soul, and return
in evening, they howl like the dog.

54:20.023 --> 54:23.525
"Thou shall bury the evils,
and they will walk the Earth no more.

54:24.464 --> 54:29.417
"Because of thy strength I will wait
for thee, for God is my high tower."

54:34.901 --> 54:36.820
It's working!

54:36.924 --> 54:38.994
Hey, that's pretty good.

54:39.098 --> 54:41.730
Hey. It worked.

54:43.107 --> 54:45.756
- I can still hear them.
- There's one more part here,

54:45.860 --> 54:48.352
- then they should be gone.
- Don't get so close.

54:48.457 --> 54:50.485
- It's okay. It's working.
- Get back!

54:50.589 --> 54:52.914
Don't be such a...

54:57.497 --> 54:59.207
- Terry!
- Terry!

54:59.311 --> 55:01.948
What are we gonna do? Terry!

55:03.731 --> 55:06.639
- Terry!
- Terry!

55:07.382 --> 55:09.907
- Terry!
- Terry!

55:10.011 --> 55:11.716
Hey!

55:16.181 --> 55:17.997
Where is he?

55:18.101 --> 55:20.162
- Hi.
- Hey.

55:36.264 --> 55:40.033
No! Terry! Answer me!

55:40.346 --> 55:43.105
Terry! Answer me!

55:43.209 --> 55:45.002
Help! Glen!

55:48.756 --> 55:51.238
- It's not gonna work!
- Glen! Help me!

55:51.342 --> 55:52.613
Come on!

55:55.228 --> 55:56.671
Let go!

55:58.912 --> 56:00.798
No!

56:15.407 --> 56:18.505
Help! Get me out of here!

56:20.705 --> 56:22.663
Help!

56:24.103 --> 56:26.255
Here he comes!

56:27.149 --> 56:29.273
Get it over here!

56:33.134 --> 56:36.342
- Terry! Grab it!
- Where's the Bible?

56:36.446 --> 56:39.364
- I can't reach it!
- "Deliver me from my enemies,

56:39.469 --> 56:40.527
father in heaven.

56:40.631 --> 56:43.696
- Stop it!
- "Deliver me from the workers of iniquity.

56:43.800 --> 56:47.409
- Glen, stop!
- "The devil's of blood.

56:48.139 --> 56:51.061
- For those who lay...
- Glen, stop it!

56:51.166 --> 56:54.359
- You're making them mad!
- Glen, grab my feet!

56:54.463 --> 56:57.731
- Hurry! I'm falling!
- Get it down here farther!

56:57.835 --> 57:00.839
- Glen, help!
- What are we gonna do?

57:02.361 --> 57:04.696
- Got it!
- Hang on!

57:04.800 --> 57:07.617
- Pull me up!
- Hold it!

57:20.816 --> 57:23.382
- Come on!
- It's closing!

57:28.950 --> 57:31.399
- Hurry!
- Come on!

57:31.503 --> 57:34.523
- Pull!
- Hurry up!

57:34.727 --> 57:37.772
My shoe! I lost my shoe!

57:38.293 --> 57:41.272
Wait... Bible. Where's the Bible?

57:44.111 --> 57:47.489
- I don't know what to read.
- Read anything!

57:52.078 --> 57:56.332
"In the beginning, God created
the heavens and the Earth."

57:56.958 --> 57:58.686
Shit.

58:43.983 --> 58:45.673
- It's gone!
